snippet.title: Tiny Heroes "Hold the Line" Walkthrough
snippet.description:
The Tiny Heroes "Hold the Line" Walkthrough.  You can tell them... you held the line.

Tiny Heroes (released September 2011) is a tower defense game for the iPhone, by award-winning game developer David Whatley, creator of Game of the Year geoDefense!

http://tinyheroes.com
